i-MSCP OwnDDNS plugin ChangeLog
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    - Fixed: Bind db entry will not deleted after deleting OwnDDNS account
    - Fixed: Disabled items must not be counted by the getCountRequests() method

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    - Fixed: No update on bind DNS server

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    - Changed: Plugin DNS record owner name from 'ownddns_feature' to 'OwnDDNS_Plugin'
    - Changed: Plugin now use the database migration API provided by i-MSCP
    - Changed: Plugin now using account name blacklist which can be defined in the config.php
    - Fixed: TTL for OwnDDNS TXT DNS record must be set to a low value to allow faster key renewal (time [default: 60] can be changed in config.php)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    - First Release
